:"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"24682","username":"haruhiの","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"24382","dbdateline":"1602297474","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"49038051","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"wuliaozheX","authorid":"389976","dateline":"2020-10-13 12:44","message":"<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://i.loli.net/2020/10/13/PTxinWKuUNH1qvO.png\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nhttps://twitter.com/Adan_iMas/status/1315711164161036288?s=19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/037.png\" />大帝，恐怖<br />\n<br />\n—— 来自 HUAWEI TEL-AN00a, Android 10上的 <a href=\"https://github.com/ykrank/S1-Next/releases\">S1Next-鹅版</a> v2.4.3","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"24683","username":"wuliaozheX","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"24383","dbdateline":"1602564273","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"49046934","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"太二EricGuo","authorid":"500388","dateline":"2020-10-14 12:01","message":"池袋西口公园第二集开幕雷击，南中人落泪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 能搜索的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"24684","username":"太二EricGuo","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"24384","dbdateline":"1602648064","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"49056957","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"skumi","authorid":"523776","dateline":"2020-10-15 13:57","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=48999120&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">ribbon 发表于 2020-10-9 16:25</font></a><br />\r\n我想要造个长句才行，反正我是想象不出来怎么几个字就说清楚丽奈姿势的。 ...</div><br />\n还原一下翻译当时的场景就是：这里讲清楚太麻烦算了算了，略过。<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/021.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要用中文还原原文的语境和语感需要长时间积累，像之前这种看到没人翻只能自己上，翻译经验又少的，翻出来还是有差距。翻得差是事实，至于把其他观点和事实混淆在一起，大可不必。<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"24685","username":"skumi","adminid":"0","groupid":"27","memberstatus":"0","number":"24385","dbdateline":"1602741458","groupiconid":"3"},{"pid":"49064448","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"ribbon","authorid":"180289","dateline":"2020-10-16 10:45","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=49056957&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">skumi 发表于 2020-10-15 13:57</font></a><br />\r\n还原一下翻译当时的场景就是：这里讲清楚太麻烦算了算了，略过。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要用中文还原原文的语境和语感需 ...</div><br />\n合着提醒下读者不要被译者带节奏都不行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我本来是挑出了7、8条翻译错误的，最后写出来的只是最严重和最轻微的两个而已，还有不知所云的，阴阳怪气的，睁眼说瞎话的等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n后来想想算了，人家用爱发电，要求太高没必要，这个不用你来告诉我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我说明白点好了，绝大部分的翻译问题，都集中在高黄身上，译者是什么心态我懒得评价。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"24686","username":"ribbon","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"24386","dbdateline":"1602816321","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"49064706","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2020-10-16 11:09","message":"<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />还整翻译带节奏呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我还说波乱前篇结尾省掉了三年级长号前辈落选的段落，是不是翻译对长号组有特别的感情啊","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"24687","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"24387","dbdateline":"1602817745","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"49066038","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"loley","authorid":"527064","dateline":"2020-10-16 13:21","message":"我也是梦到过伞哥哥的人了！在梦中为伞哥哥辩护！","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"24688","username":"loley","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"24388","dbdateline":"1602825710","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"49068974","